The '''rock golem''' can be found in the [[Enchanted Valley]], accessible using the fairy ring code {{fairycode|BKQ}}, appearing when attempting to mine a rock. The rock golem will use [[Ranged]] attacks and [[Protect from Missiles]] will negate all damage.

Before the [[random event]] update in [[2014]], the rock golem used to appear randomly when [[Mining]]. Upon appearing, it would say {{RSChat|Raarrrgghh! Flee human!}} As with similar guardian random events, the rock golem's [[combat level]] and stats scaled with the player's combat level, as well as only being attackable by the targeted player.

==Levels==
The rock golem's combat level when it appears is dependent on the player's own combat level.

